Languages and Frameworks used: Java, Spring-boot, JUnit, Mockito

Features included:
1. Endpoint /api/ping works.
2. Endpoint /api/posts fetches Hatchway API one tag at a time, asynchronously.
3. Fetched list of posts are not repeated and sorted by property received by endpoint.
4. The results are stored and retrieved in cache memory.

